The Resistance (Time-Life World War II Series)
Time-Life Books | 1998 | ISBN 0783557116 | English | 216 pages | PDF | 31.7 MB

An account of resistance groups, members, and activities in Nazi-occupied Europe. This volume is full of great color and B&W photos, maps, and narratives of resistance against the Axis in France, Denmark, Luxembourg, the Netherlands, Belgium, and Norway
